ee.adit.service
Class MonitorService

java.lang.Object
  ee.adit.service.MonitorService

public class MonitorService
extends java.lang.Object

Provides monitoring services. Monitoring consist of the following: 1. Check database read 2. Check database write 3. Check application settings (temporary folder)

Author:
Marko Kurm, Microlink Eesti AS, marko.kurm@microlink.ee
